title: Earthy Eating Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Western, Juice bar
description: Little cafe offering seasonal menus with all food being gluten free and without refined sugar. Variety of raw meals and raw cakes; bowls and breakfast foods like house-made granola and fruit with coconut cream bowls; fruit smoothies made with house-made almond milk or coconut water; raw savory tarts made with activated nuts and seeds topped with salsa and served with salad.
streetAddress: Shop 15a Marriott Waters Shopping Centre, Thompsons Rd
